{
  "name": "CF1-Reset-Demo",
  "description": "Manual reversal playbook. Removes every OneFlare demo artifact created by the CF1-* playbooks so the Cloudflare portal is clean for the next demo: deletes zone IP access rules, custom-firewall (Ruleset) rules, and Gateway DNS rules whose notes/description/name contain \"OneFlare\"; deletes the sinkhole DNS record; and reverts zone security level to medium. Idempotent (missing artifacts are no-ops). Bind the Cloudflare connection, then run manually.",
